Q-23) Print the first N natural numbers using recursion.
Input Format
One number, N.
Constraints
1 <= N <= 1000
Output Format
The first N natural numbers separated by a space. They must be printed using a recursive function only.
Sample Input 0
3
Sample Output 0
1 2 3

CODE:

#include<stdio.h>  
void display(int); 
int main()  
{  
    int limit;  
    scanf("%d", &limit);  
    display(limit);  
    return 0;  
}  
void display(int num)  
{  
    if(num)  
        display(num-1);  
    else  
        return;  
    printf("%d ", num); 
}
